I"¾<p>Integrates MySensors binary sensors into Home Assistant. See the <a href="/integrations/mysensors/">main component</a> for configuration instructions.</p>
<p>The following sensor types are supported:</p>
<h4>MySensors version 1.4 and higher</h4>
<table>
<thead>
<tr>
<th>S_TYPE</th>
<th>V_TYPE</th>
</tr>
</thead>
<tbody>
<tr>
<td>S_DOOR</td>
<td>V_TRIPPED</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td>S_MOTION</td>
<td>V_TRIPPED</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td>S_SMOKE</td>
<td>V_TRIPPED</td>
</tr>
</tbody>
</table>
<h4>MySensors version 1.5 and higher</h4>
<table>
<thead>
<tr>
<th>S_TYPE</th>
<th>V_TYPE</th>
</tr>
</thead>
<tbody>
<tr>
<td>S_SPRINKLER</td>
<td>V_TRIPPED</td>
</tr>
<tr>
